<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="50" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[701,1298,694,1117]" pageId="1" pageNumber="50">Type specimen was collected from Holocene deposits from the Bird's Head Peninsula, West Papua, Indonesia. Probably most closely related to D. palpator. Monotypic.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
